title: Dark Aeon Cyber Watch Face
summary: Enhance your watch with street address, missed calls and millions of colors.

descriptionHTML:
The Dark Aeon Cyber Watch Face is here. Enhance your smartwatch time telling experience with this powerful watch face. The current street address is shown on your watch using GPS. The last missed call is shown by displaying the name of the caller or the phone number if the name is not in your contact list. The cyber aesthetic will please you with a flowing animation on the watch face.

Dark Aeon Cyber Watch Face will work well on both round and square smartwatches.

- Street Address Display
- Missed call name or number shown
- 12 and 24 hour time modes
- Multiple date formats
- watch battery level
- phone battery level
- millions of color combinations
- fully customize the appearance of the watch
- customize the two tone animation
- excellent time reading experience with Dark Aeon Cyber Watch Face

When downloading Dark Aeon Cyber Watch Face, be sure to have Android Wear installed. Android Wear is needed in order to install this watch face on to your smartwatch.

GPS Location needs to be enabled on your phone in order to retrieve GPS location data for the watch face.
